361
00:20:54,720 --> 00:20:56,799
or the scenery shown in the film,

362
00:20:56,799 --> 00:20:57,640
which touches you,

363
00:20:57,640 --> 00:21:01,799
I think you can try to do it first.

364
00:21:01,799 --> 00:21:03,400
The road is made step by step.

365
00:21:03,400 --> 00:21:04,480
The important thing is to take action,

366
00:21:04,480 --> 00:21:07,240
rather than choosing what to do.

367
00:21:08,119 --> 00:21:09,960
Whether you choose Tor des Géants

368
00:21:09,960 --> 00:21:12,279
or take a park hike,

369
00:21:12,279 --> 00:21:15,039
or even just leave home and walk to a strange street,

370
00:21:15,039 --> 00:21:16,519
these are both good things to you,

371
00:21:16,519 --> 00:21:17,920
as long as you go out and experience,

372
00:21:17,920 --> 00:21:19,119
and experience different things,

373
00:21:19,319 --> 00:21:20,359
and accumulate them gradually.

374
00:21:20,359 --> 00:21:23,000
I think you may have your own path.

375
00:21:23,000 --> 00:21:24,920
It's not about completing the Tor des Géants,

376
00:21:24,920 --> 00:21:26,720
or complete the PTL,

377
00:21:26,720 --> 00:21:28,799
as your ultimate goal.

378
00:21:28,960 --> 00:21:31,240
Don't take others' goals as your own.

379
00:21:31,240 --> 00:21:32,720
Even if you achieve it,

380
00:21:32,720 --> 00:21:35,119
you may not feel very happy.

381
00:21:35,119 --> 00:21:35,720
You may even feel,

382
00:21:35,720 --> 00:21:38,200
you may not know what to do next.

383
00:21:38,200 --> 00:21:40,480
In the process of your own exploration,

384
00:21:40,480 --> 00:21:41,640
have your own style.

385
00:21:43,000 --> 00:21:44,920
Don't think that nature is,

386
00:21:44,920 --> 00:21:47,599
may be defined as mountains, seas, lakes, and so on.

387
00:21:47,599 --> 00:21:50,720
In fact, nature is the city where you live,

388
00:21:50,720 --> 00:21:52,559
or maybe the streets where you live.

389
00:21:52,559 --> 00:21:53,480
These are all nature.

390
00:21:55,000 --> 00:21:58,519
Don't say that you only look at the world,

391
00:21:58,519 --> 00:22:01,559
only through social media,

392
00:22:01,559 --> 00:22:02,720
and see nature.

393
00:22:02,720 --> 00:22:04,920
I think the best way is to go out and experience it,

394
00:22:04,920 --> 00:22:06,000
and experience more.

395
00:22:14,039 --> 00:22:14,839
Yes.

396
00:22:15,680 --> 00:22:16,480
Oh.

397
00:22:17,119 --> 00:22:17,920
Oh.

398
00:22:46,440 --> 00:22:47,839
When I was running in early times,

399
00:22:47,839 --> 00:22:48,799
run one hundred kilometers,

400
00:22:48,799 --> 00:22:50,880
or navigate myself to Wugong Mountain,

401
00:22:50,880 --> 00:22:52,720
when I was in the forest and encountered spider webs,

402
00:22:53,079 --> 00:22:53,960
my physical strength decreased,

403
00:22:53,960 --> 00:22:55,680
and my face was covered with bugs,

404
00:22:55,680 --> 00:22:57,119
I was very frustrated when I was covered in spider webs.

405
00:22:57,880 --> 00:22:58,720
This is the mentality,

406
00:22:58,720 --> 00:23:01,119
and gradually it may transfer to,

407
00:23:01,119 --> 00:23:02,680
my current Tor des Géants.

408
00:23:02,680 --> 00:23:05,680
when facing darkness, fatigue or injury,

409
00:23:05,680 --> 00:23:08,440
I have to adjust myself.

410
00:23:08,440 --> 00:23:11,079
how to cheer up and move on to the next supply station.

411
00:23:11,119 --> 00:23:12,319
It should be the process.

412
00:23:13,079 --> 00:23:14,119
I can only say,

413
00:23:14,240 --> 00:23:16,079
the memories left by this place are so beautiful.

414
00:23:16,079 --> 00:23:18,400
This place is really beautiful.

415
00:23:18,480 --> 00:23:20,839
I will try to come back every year.

416
00:23:20,839 --> 00:23:23,920
I will still train myself,

417
00:23:23,920 --> 00:23:26,119
to make my next experence better.

418
00:23:26,279 --> 00:23:28,559
Not that I'll get better results.

419
00:23:28,559 --> 00:23:30,000
In the same time,

420
00:23:30,000 --> 00:23:31,799
I might become more calm.

421
00:23:31,799 --> 00:23:33,440
I think this is the goal I pursue.

422
00:23:38,240 --> 00:23:39,960
When I get off work every day,

423
00:23:39,960 --> 00:23:41,640
I run to the back mountain near my workplace,

424
00:23:41,759 --> 00:23:43,160
and watch the sunset from a distance.

425
00:23:43,160 --> 00:23:44,440
I can see the Qingshuijian Mountain,

426
00:23:44,440 --> 00:23:45,960
I don't think,

427
00:23:45,960 --> 00:23:47,640
the Alps are particularly important.

428
00:23:47,640 --> 00:23:49,119
I feel like this.

429
00:23:51,359 --> 00:23:53,079
Life is a,

430
00:23:53,079 --> 00:23:53,640
circle.

431
00:23:53,640 --> 00:23:55,920
Some people may draw a big circle,

432
00:23:56,079 --> 00:23:57,000
and take many paths.
